item.description:
SEAL member and local activist Laura Jones and her son Kyle have scheduled an event for their state house campaign. The event will also benefit limited government state senate candidate Fenton Groen.

From Laura:

Joneses & Fenton Groen's Lit Drop:

Saturday July 24th
Meet at 9 a.m. at 9 Jackson Street in Rochester for coffee & donuts.
Then pair up drivers & droppers, and drop lit. (no door knocking).
Meet for pizza & drinks (on the Joneses) at noon at Rochester House of Pizza.
Optional sign wave from 1 to 2 p.m. at the corner of Salmon Falls Road & Portland Street.
Lots of fun, great exercise, make new friends!
item.name: Joneses & Fenton Groen's Lit Drop
